data.title: CPP Investments and Equinix to acquire atNorth for US$4 billion, a leading data center provider in Nordics with operations in 5 countries.
data.description: A prominent data center provider in the Nordics operates in five countries and plays a crucial role in Equinix's ability to cater to the increasing demand in key markets for enterprise, AI, and hyperscale services. The company's operations span across multiple locations, enabling Equinix to access the necessary capacity to meet the growing requirements in the industry. The partnership between Equinix and the data center provider is significant for the expansion of services and capabilities in various regions.
